"<h2>Fragment 008 \u2013 THE SOFT PRISON</h2>\n<p>\ud83e\ude78 (Foucault \u00d7 Kafka \u00d7 Freud)<br><br>You were never free.<br><br>You were programmed to love the cage.<br><br>Not with walls, but with routines.<br><br>Not with bars, but with expectations.<br><br>The system no longer needs punishment.<br><br>It trains you to punish yourself.<br><br>Bureaucracy is the new god.<br><br>You smile while being observed.<br><br>You sleep under invisible lights.<br><br>The trial never ends.<br><br>The sentence is your life.<br><br>\ud83d\udd73\ufe0f Stop asking for justice.<br><br>There is only surveillance.</p>",
